==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Manufactory
<hw>Man`u*fac"to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>-ries</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Cf. L. <ets>factorium</ets>
